  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large dolsot over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onions and cook until they start to caramelize, about 8 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced ginger and cook for another 2 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced Kenyan chilies and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped spinach and cook until it starts to wilt, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the diced sweet potatoes, salt, black pepper, and smoked paprika. Stir well to combine.",
    "Cook for 10-12 minutes or until the sweet potatoes are cooked through and the spinach is fully wilted.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional chopped spinach if desired."
